# Security — vibe-security skill

Before shipping or refactoring anything that touches **authentication (Clerk)**, **Supabase**, **secrets / env**, **API routes**, **payments**, **webhooks**, **AI/API keys**, or **user-controlled input**, load the project skill:

- [.cursor/skills/vibe-security/SKILL.md](../skills/vibe-security/SKILL.md)

Follow its audit checklist and pull in the referenced files under `.cursor/skills/vibe-security/references/` only for technologies in use.

**Baseline:** Never trust the client; enforce authorization and secrets only on trusted servers; enable and scope Supabase RLS with `WITH CHECK`; never expose `service_role` in browser bundles (`VITE_`, etc.).
